            "body": "Need to be clear about what we mean here. \"range only\" is not really an actual concept, it's just a name we are giving to things like \":1\".\n\n```suggestion\n  // Commands such as \":1\" are \"range only\" commands.\n  bool range_only = ea.cmdidx == CMD_SIZE && cmd->cmd.data[0] == NUL\n```",
