            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "using `nvim_parse_cmd` here kind of defeats the purpose, no?\n```suggestion\n      eq('', api.nvim_cmd({ cmd = 'noautocmd', ... }, {}), {}))\n```",
            "commit_id": "422fb40f384c25181fc814bbb39c4fd31a58b9b3",
            "created_at": "2026-03-12T14:04:23Z",
            "diff_hunk": "@@ -5209,6 +5257,9 @@ describe('API', function()\n       -- error from the next command typed is not suppressed #21420\n       feed(':call<CR><CR>')\n       eq('E471: Argument required', api.nvim_cmd({ cmd = 'messages' }, { output = true }))\n+\n+      -- modifier only\n+      eq('', api.nvim_cmd(api.nvim_parse_cmd('noautocmd', {}), {}))",
